xxl.core.io.fat.util
Interface DataManagement

All Known Implementing Classes:
InorderTraverse
public interface DataManagement

This interface is used to manage some kind of data. The implementation classes of this interface can be a stack or a queue for instance. This will change the order the data objects are used.
